            <title>[DATAREST-394] Projections are not applied to collection attributes</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-394</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a projection has an attribute which is a collection of another projection, Spring Data REST is not populating the collection with projections but with entities. This patch allows Spring Data REST to apply projections to collection attributes as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
